data.description: Welcome to 3702 Sandbar Dr, located in the highly sought-after Super Mill Plantation. This stunning home offers 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and an impressive 2,573 square feet of living space, making it the perfect sanctuary for your family. As you step through the custom 9-foot doors, you'll be captivated by the spacious and open floor plan that awaits you. The grand dining room on your left effortlessly flows into the expansive living room, adorned with elegant crown molding throughout, creating an atmosphere of sophistication and comfort. Prepare to be amazed by the immense kitchen, truly a chef's dream come true. It boasts a remarkable waterfall island, providing both style and functionality, and an abundance of storage space that seems never-ending. Cooking becomes a pleasure with the convenience of a built-in pot filler, making your culinary endeavors a breeze. The kitchen also features a bright breakfast nook, allowing you to enjoy the beauty of natural lighting while savoring your meals. The master bedroom and bathroom will leave you in awe. The spacious bedroom exudes peace and tranquility, providing the perfect retreat at the end of a long day. The master bathroom is a true masterpiece with its dual vanities, separate shower, and luxurious garden soaking tub, creating a spa-like experience in the comfort of your own home. And that's not all; the bathroom leads into an expansive walk-in closet, fulfilling all your storage needs. The additional three bedrooms are generously sized, each offering ample closet space to accommodate your family's needs comfortably. This home is designed to cater to your lifestyle, ensuring everyone has their own space and privacy. The backyard offers endless potential, providing a blank canvas for you to create the outdoor oasis of your dreams.  Moreover, this home comes equipped with a whole-home generator, offering peace of mind during power outages. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite residence your own.
